import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Form, FormGroup, InputGroup, FormLabel, Button } from "react-bootstrap"

class App extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Form>
        <FormGroup>
          <FormLabel for="name">Name:</FormLabel>
          <InputGroup
            type="text"
            name="name"
            onChange={this.handleChange} />
        </FormGroup>

        <FormGroup>
          <FormLabel for="email">Email:</FormLabel>
          <InputGroup
            type="email"
            name="email"
            onChange={this.handleChange} />
        </FormGroup>

        <FormGroup>
          <FormLabel for="message">Message:</FormLabel>
          <InputGroup
            type="textarea"
            name="message"
            onChange={this.handleChange} />

            <Button>Submit</Button>
        </FormGroup>
      </Form>

    );
  }
}

export default App;
